pro2E.model

Class Radiator

  • java.lang.Object
    • pro2E.model.Radiator

  • public class Radiator
extends java.lang.Object
     The Radiator class represents a radiator in an antenna array and therefore stores all its relevant parameters.
 Furthermore it contains various methods to manipulate those parameters.
    Author:
    pro2E - Team3
